00:00:50,434 --> 00:00:51,626
Rosye.

13
00:00:51,615 --> 00:00:52,672
familye?

14
00:00:52,459 --> 00:00:53,870
Semetski.

15
00:00:57,657 --> 00:01:01,830
dos, dos iz di karte fun Tshernevits.

16
00:01:02,027 --> 00:01:04,320
mir hobn zikh fotografirt

17
00:01:04,525 --> 00:01:08,754
vayl mayn shvoger hot gebetn fun Yisroel fun undz a karte.

18
00:01:09,351 --> 00:01:11,370
dos iz mayn man, Leyzer,

19
00:01:11,612 --> 00:01:15,440
dos iz Khanele Melamed,

20
00:01:15,915 --> 00:01:17,579
un dos bin ikh.

21
00:01:19,054 --> 00:01:23,975
zeyer sheyne kartes. m'hot zikh zeyer gevundert in Yisroel,

22
00:01:24,555 --> 00:01:29,594
ven mayn shvoger hot arayngetrogn tsum balebos, vu er hot gearbet, di karte.

23
00:01:29,719 --> 00:01:32,719
er hot gezogt, "gib a kuk vi in Rusland

24
00:01:32,719 --> 00:01:34,927
zeen di mentshn oys!"

25
00:01:38,376 --> 00:01:39,815
di karte

26
00:01:39,815 --> 00:01:44,782
hobn mir arayngekrign fun Yisroel, fun mayn shvegerin un fun mayn shvoger.

27
00:01:45,733 --> 00:01:49,130
zey hobn undz aroysgenemen keyn Amerike.

28
00:01:49,130 --> 00:01:51,636
m'hot undz fil guts geton.

29
00:01:51,636 --> 00:01:54,320
dos iz mayn shvoger, Kalmen Melamed,

30
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:56,200
un Dore Melamed.

31
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:59,306
zey hobn zeyer a sakh far undz geton,

32
00:01:59,306 --> 00:02:02,610
biz zey hobn undz ayngeordnt in Tshernevits...

33
00:02:03,132 --> 00:02:04,425
in Amerike.

34
00:02:06,338 --> 00:02:06,855
⟨nu⟩

35
00:02:07,907 --> 00:02:11,844
di karte hot men gemakht bay RICHARDl JACOB

36
00:02:11,844 --> 00:02:14,145
oyfn, oyf der bar-mitsve.

37
00:02:14,843 --> 00:02:18,696
do zitsn mayne ale eynikes.

38
00:02:18,696 --> 00:02:22,200
finef barlyantishe yingelekh hob ikh.

39
00:02:22,757 --> 00:02:25,120
kent ir rufn yed⟨ern⟩ fun zey ⟨on⟩?

40
00:02:22,909 --> 00:02:23,909
der,

41
00:02:24,158 --> 00:02:27,223
der eltster heyst RICHARD JACOB.

42
00:02:26,824 --> 00:02:27,813
vu iz er?

43
00:02:27,853 --> 00:02:29,790
der. der...

44
00:02:29,558 --> 00:02:32,240
 fun velkhn zayt iz er? in mitn.

45
00:02:29,862 --> 00:02:30,970
der groyser.

46
00:02:32,646 --> 00:02:34,175
der tsveyter

47
00:02:34,283 --> 00:02:36,302
iz STUIE JACOB.

48
00:02:36,595 --> 00:02:37,719
vu shteyt er?

49
00:02:37,557 --> 00:02:38,860
er shteyt,

50
00:02:39,447 --> 00:02:41,595
der, der blonder bokher,

51
00:02:41,595 --> 00:02:44,130
lebn BRIANen shteyt er.

52
00:02:44,307 --> 00:02:48,131
der driter iz Dani, Daniel, mitn roytn bantikl.

53
00:02:48,576 --> 00:02:50,173
dos iz der driter.

54
00:02:50,820 --> 00:02:54,410
der ferder shteyt lebn mayn man, BRIAN

55
00:02:54,904 --> 00:02:56,310
Sapir.

56
00:02:56,541 --> 00:02:58,425
un dos kleyntshike

57
00:02:58,633 --> 00:03:02,160
iz mole-tam. er iz azoy klug!

58
00:03:02,380 --> 00:03:04,281
Erik Sapir.

59
00:03:04,388 --> 00:03:05,870
un dos iz mayn...

60
00:03:04,422 --> 00:03:06,188
un ver zitst do?

61
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:09,697
un dos iz mayn man, Leyzer Melamed,

62
00:03:09,973 --> 00:03:12,900
un ikh, mit ale eyniklekh,

63
00:03:12,900 --> 00:03:15,789
sheyne, goldene kinder mayne.

64
00:03:16,791 --> 00:03:17,780
s'iz gut?

65
00:03:19,457 --> 00:03:21,440
in der linker zayt,

66
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:23,673
s'klenste eynikl mayns,

67
00:03:23,673 --> 00:03:27,600
Erikl. in gikhn vel'mir hobn zayn bar-mitsve,

68
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:32,479
in a guter sho. di mame mitn tatn zol hobn a sakh nakhes fun im.

69
00:03:33,345 --> 00:03:37,350
un den iz di tokhter mayne, Zoyele Sapir,

70
00:03:37,918 --> 00:03:40,159
zeyer a sheyne un a gute,

71
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:43,030
zol hobn a sakh nakhes fun ire kinder.

72
00:03:43,268 --> 00:03:45,776
dos iz BRIAle, der driter,

73
00:03:45,816 --> 00:03:46,974
BRIAN,

74
00:03:47,487 --> 00:03:50,300
a sheyner bokher, a guter.

75
00:03:50,659 --> 00:03:52,920
un dos iz mayn eydem, Mark,

76
00:03:53,055 --> 00:03:56,047
a voyler eydem. er zol zayn gezunt

77
00:03:56,047 --> 00:03:58,630
un hobn nakhes fun zayne kinder,

78
00:03:58,630 --> 00:04:01,115
un mir zol'mir hobn nakhes fun zey.

79
00:04:01,678 --> 00:04:05,570
dos iz mayn eltster eynik fun der kleyner tokhter,

80
00:04:06,623 --> 00:04:07,984
Danyele.

81
00:04:08,513 --> 00:04:11,430
zeyer a guter, a gutn kop.

82
00:04:11,430 --> 00:04:15,510
er lernt zeyer gut. er geyt dos ershte yor in kaledzh.

83
00:04:15,921 --> 00:04:20,140
den zitst mayn man, Leyzer Melamed,

84
00:04:20,140 --> 00:04:25,220
un ikh zits tsvishn mayn sheyner FAMILY Sapir.

85
00:04:31,193 --> 00:04:35,970
in der linker zayt shteyt mayn eltste tokhter, Khanele.

86
00:04:37,757 --> 00:04:41,328
azoyne kinder iz keyn sakh oyf der velt nishto.

87
00:04:42,162 --> 00:04:44,788
in der rekhter zayt shteyt mayn eydem,

88
00:04:45,115 --> 00:04:48,290
oykhet zeyer a guter, a voyler.

89
00:04:48,507 --> 00:04:52,584
in der rekhter zayt shteyt mayn eltster eynik, RICHele.

90
00:04:52,827 --> 00:04:57,276
er lernt in kaledzh, er FINISHt dos yor dem kaledzh,

91
00:04:57,433 --> 00:04:59,587
un er iz zeyer BEAUTIFUL.

92
00:05:00,825 --> 00:05:08,176
in der linker zayt, dos blonde yingele, iz STUyele, mayn tokhter's der eltster's kleyne yingele.

93
00:05:08,622 --> 00:05:14,319
zeyer a vazhner bokher, POSTUPet in kaledzh, un er vet geyn dos yor in kaledzh.

94
00:05:14,410 --> 00:05:16,946
a sakh nakhes zol ikh hobn fun aykh.

95
00:05:16,946 --> 00:05:19,342
zolst mir zayn gezunt, tokhter mayne,

96
00:05:19,342 --> 00:05:22,504
vayl du bist krank, zolst mir zayn gezunt.

97
00:05:26,570 --> 00:05:28,022
RICHele.

98
00:05:28,399 --> 00:05:31,397
dos iz dayn tog fun der bar-mitsve.

99
00:05:31,926 --> 00:05:34,893
ikh zol hobn fun dir a sakh nakhes.

100
00:05:34,893 --> 00:05:36,560
kh'hob dikh zeyer lib.

101
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:38,535
du bist mayn gants lebn.

102
00:05:39,621 --> 00:05:44,200
zolst hobn a gut lebn, un got zol dir helfn, vos du vilst.

103
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:47,191
nakhes zoln dayne eltern hobn fun dir.

104
00:05:48,042 --> 00:05:50,140
zay gezunt, yingele.

105
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:50,196
vi iz zayn familye?

106
00:05:52,648 --> 00:05:53,654
JACOB.

107
00:05:54,184 --> 00:05:55,730
RICHARD JACOB.

108
00:05:57,660 --> 00:06:00,590
dos iz Danye Sh- Sapir.

109
00:06:00,951 --> 00:06:04,303
dos iz der eltster eynik fun mayn kleyner tokhter,

110
00:06:04,427 --> 00:06:07,528
der tog fun der bar-mitsve, in shil.

111
00:06:07,528 --> 00:06:11,322
a sakh nakhes zol dayn mame mit dayn tatn hobn fun dir.

112
00:06:11,413 --> 00:06:14,208
zolst zay- nemen a yidish meydele,

113
00:06:14,282 --> 00:06:17,450
un zolst aleyn haltn a bisl yidishkeyt.

114
00:06:17,450 --> 00:06:21,300
Danyele, zay gezunt, un nakhes fun dir.

115
00:06:23,935 --> 00:06:25,988
dos iz STUIE JACOB,

116
00:06:26,905 --> 00:06:30,257
der tsveyter zun mayn tokhter der eltster's.

117
00:06:31,545 --> 00:06:33,125
er iz in shil.

118
00:06:35,646 --> 00:06:37,510
a PICTURE sheyne,

119
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:42,317
a guter bokher. zol hobn nakhes fun dir dayne eltern,

120
00:06:42,317 --> 00:06:45,579
un zolst geyn oyf a rikhtikn PU- veg.

121
00:06:50,260 --> 00:06:53,790
di karte iz fun BRIAN Sapir.

122
00:06:54,867 --> 00:06:57,662
a sheyner bokher, a oytserisher.

123
00:06:58,090 --> 00:07:00,733
er iz fotografirt in shil.

124
00:07:03,777 --> 00:07:08,293
vos zol ikh zogn vayter fun im? veys ikh gornit... zol hobn a sakh nakhes fun im.

125
00:07:08,873 --> 00:07:13,896
sheyn bistu vi zibn veltn. aza mazl zolstu hobn vi ⟨b- bay⟩ mir in di oygn.

126
00:07:17,260 --> 00:07:19,480
Erik Sapir.

127
00:07:20,820 --> 00:07:22,906
in a por monatn arum,

128
00:07:22,913 --> 00:07:26,214
sheyn yingele mayns, vel'mir hobn dayn bar-mitsve.

129
00:07:26,727 --> 00:07:30,788
di mame mitn tatn un mir zol'mir hobn a sakh nakhes fun dir,

130
00:07:30,895 --> 00:07:32,970
un zolst zayn a voyl yingl.

131
00:07:33,730 --> 00:07:35,462
shoyn. geFINISHt fun im.

132
00:07:41,172 --> 00:07:42,904
in der linker zayt

133
00:07:43,112 --> 00:07:45,880
shteyt mayn eltster eynik

134
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:47,606
fun der kleyner tokhter,

135
00:07:47,606 --> 00:07:49,610
D- Dani Sapir,

136
00:07:49,930 --> 00:07:53,850
un den shteyt Zoye Sapir lebn im,

137
00:07:55,465 --> 00:07:58,446
un den shteyt NATHAN JACOB,

138
00:07:58,452 --> 00:08:01,270
mayn eydem fun der eltster tokhter.

139
00:08:02,012 --> 00:08:04,537
oyfn benkl zitst mayn eydem,

140
00:08:04,662 --> 00:08:06,371
Mark Sapir.

141
00:08:06,371 --> 00:08:09,735
lebn im shteyt dos kleyne yingele zayns,

142
00:08:09,758 --> 00:08:11,660
Erik Sapir.

143
00:08:13,015 --> 00:08:19,520
un lebn mayn eydem, lebn eltstn, shteyt mayn tokhter, di groyse, Khanele JACOB.

144
00:08:20,912 --> 00:08:24,703
in der rekhter zayt shteyt mayn man, Leyzer Melamed.

145
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:31,080
RICHARD JACOB, der eltster eynik fun mayn, groyser tokhter.

146
00:08:31,527 --> 00:08:33,546
ikh zits oyfn benkl.

147
00:08:34,006 --> 00:08:36,649
den shteyt STUIE JACOB,

148
00:08:36,707 --> 00:08:38,878
mayn eltster tokhter's zun,

149
00:08:39,778 --> 00:08:41,884
un se shteyt BRIAN,

150
00:08:41,884 --> 00:08:43,822
der kleyner tokhter's zun,

151
00:08:44,098 --> 00:08:45,796
BRIAN Sapir.

152
00:08:45,853 --> 00:08:48,007
dos iz di familye mayne,

153
00:08:48,098 --> 00:08:50,280
vos got hot mir geholfn.

154
00:08:50,280 --> 00:08:53,340
ikh bin gekumen krik fun UNK lager,

155
00:08:53,346 --> 00:08:56,327
vos mentshn zenen gefaln vi shtroy,

156
00:08:56,772 --> 00:08:59,280
un ikh hob gekont bay mayn lebn

157
00:08:59,607 --> 00:09:03,578
nokh makhn aza FAMILY, aza sheyne FAMILY,

158
00:09:03,578 --> 00:09:06,960
vos der daytsh hot undz gevolt oyskoylen

159
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,125
ile yidn,

160
00:09:08,125 --> 00:09:11,514
un dank got oyf aykh, vos mir ho'mir gekont

161
00:09:11,537 --> 00:09:14,320
hobn nokh aza sheyne FAMILY.

162
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:17,320
zey zoln derlebn nakhes fun zeyere kinder,

163
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:21,730
un zoln dertseyln dos vos di bobe mitn zeydn hot ibergelebt.

164
00:09:21,831 --> 00:09:25,743
zayt mir gezunt, kinderlekh, un gedenkt az der tate

165
00:09:25,743 --> 00:09:29,286
mit der mamen hobn ibergelebt a shvern lager.

166
00:09:29,286 --> 00:09:32,222
dos darft ir zogn ayere kinder oykh,

167
00:09:32,222 --> 00:09:34,281
zey zoln visn az zey zenen yidn,

168
00:09:34,281 --> 00:09:36,236
un zey darfn nemen yidn.

169
00:09:38,571 --> 00:09:39,620
nu, g-...

